{"about_the_game":"Collect and hatch eggs. Delegate dragons on epic expeditions on which they will fight an auto battle for loot and goodies. Build your dragons with diverse evolutions, perks, amulets, and more! <br>Complete quests to unlock new features. Participate in 3 vs 3 battles during dungeons, designed with roguelite mode in mind, for the best loot possible. Increase the number of dragons to optimize your income and progress. Take your time to max out amulets in the blacksmith, manage funds carefully to avoid inflation, collect all the collectables to fulfill your gallery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WATCH YOUR DRAGONS FIGHT ON YOUR COMMAND</strong></h2>Your dragons will battle on variety of adventures and dungeons. Train and upgrade them for the toughest challenges!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598630/extras/battle_4.gif?t=1729772847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>COLLECT AND EQUIP AMULETS</strong></h2>Choose from over 50 amulets to create a unique path for your dragon. Take the highest quality ones to become a real raid boss.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598630/extras/skull.png?t=1729772847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>HATCH AND UPGRADE</strong></h2>Discover 30+ dragons, with some evolving into 26 unique forms and upgrade their TIER to unlock new dragon upgrades!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598630/extras/s.png?t=1729772847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CHOSE YOUR PLAYSTYLE</strong></h2>Each dragon has a unique perk tree to suit various playstyles and counterplay enemies. Discover over 100 unique effects!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598630/extras/wildgrowth.png?t=1729772847\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite